## Key Blog System Components

**Core Pages:**
- Blog listing, individual posts, topic pages
- 4 layout templates (center, grid, split-left, split-right)

**Content:**
- 20 markdown blog posts
- 12 metadata JSON files for structured data

**Components:**
- 30 Blog components for UI/UX
- Homepage sections for blog integration

**Logic:**
- 7 utility libraries for blog operations
- Comment API, newsletter hooks, validation

**Scripts:**
- 9 maintenance scripts for SEO/content management
